   <ext_description linkend="Constructive_solid_geometry_2d_mim"/>
   
   <ext_description linkend="Constructive_solid_geometry_2d_mim.csg_2d_shape_representation">
   A <b>csg_2d_shape_representation</b> is a type of <express_ref linkend="product_property_representation_schema:ir_express:product_property_representation_schema.shape_representation"/> that
implements the ARM concept of <express_ref linkend="Constructive_solid_geometry_2d:arm:Constructive_solid_geometry_2d_arm.Csg_2d_model"/>.
A <b>csg_2d_shape_representation</b> is a two-dimensional <express_ref linkend="product_property_representation_schema:ir_express:product_property_representation_schema.shape_representation"/> that represents the shape of a product using constructive solid geometry operations and techniques. The solid objects may be either 2D primitives, or half-space 2D solids. 
   </ext_description>
   <ext_description linkend="Constructive_solid_geometry_2d_mim.csg_2d_shape_representation.wr:WR1">
   The <express_ref linkend="geometry_schema:ir_express:geometry_schema.geometric_representation_context"/> of the <b>csg_2d_shape_representation</b> shall have a <express_ref linkend="geometry_schema:ir_express:geometry_schema.geometric_representation_context.coordinate_space_dimension"/> equal to two.
   </ext_description>
   <ext_description linkend="Constructive_solid_geometry_2d_mim.csg_2d_shape_representation.wr:WR2">
   The items in a <b>csg_2d_shape_representation</b> shall be a <express_ref linkend="geometric_model_schema:ir_express:geometric_model_schema.csg_solid"/>, <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item"/>, or an <express_ref linkend="geometry_schema:ir_express:geometry_schema.axis2_placement_2d"/>. 
   </ext_description>
   <ext_description linkend="Constructive_solid_geometry_2d_mim.csg_2d_shape_representation.wr:WR3">
   At least one of the items in a <b>csg_2d_shape_representation</b> shall be a <express_ref linkend="geometric_model_schema:ir_express:geometric_model_schema.csg_solid"/>, or a <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item"/> with a <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation_map.mapped_representation"/> of the <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item.mapping_source"/> attribute of the type <b>csg_2d_shape_representation</b>. 
   </ext_description>
   <ext_description linkend="Constructive_solid_geometry_2d_mim.csg_2d_shape_representation.wr:WR4">
   If a <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item"/> is in the items set then the <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.representation_map.mapped_representation"/> of the <express_ref linkend="representation_schema:ir_express:representation_schema.mapped_item.mapping_source"/> attribute shall be a <b>csg_2d_shape_representation</b>.
   </ext_description>
   <ext_description linkend="Constructive_solid_geometry_2d_mim.csg_2d_shape_representation.wr:WR5">
   The <b>csg_2d_shape_representation</b> shall not be another type of <express_ref linkend="product_property_representation_schema:ir_express:product_property_representation_schema.shape_representation"/>.
   </ext_description>
</ext_descriptions>